text: aws graviton 2 processors changed the
game by providing thousands of customers
with up to 40 better price performance
in amazon ec2 for a broad range of
workloads
now by partnering with nvidia aws is
extending the benefits of graviton 2 to
android gaming and machine learning
developers
aws has built the first arm-based
instances in a major cloud to provide
gpu acceleration with amazon ec2 g5g
instances these feature graviton 2
processors and nvidia t4g tensor core
gpus
developers can build android games
natively encode the rendered graphics
and stream to a mobile device without
needing to run emulation software or
cross-compilation on x86 based instances
machine learning developers can also use
g5g instances to run cost-effective
inference while leveraging nvidia's
libraries
get started today with amazon ec2 g5g
instances
